---
// Client-clean narrative. Bio detail woven from LinkedIn + the book (brief §1).
---
<section class="becoming" id="about">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div>
      <span class="kicker">The becoming</span>
      <h2>From the missile field to the Court of the Table.</h2>
      <p>I left home at twelve and have been building myself ever since — a ranch, the United States Air Force, a kitchen, a sales floor. The Air Force gave me a standard and a set of men who held it. The rest I earned the hard way.</p>
      <p>What I do now is move people, money, and systems forward — and I write it all down as it happens. Not the polished retrospective. The field notes of someone still in it.</p>
      <p>I tasted the world and came home to serve the people who build this country. The debt stops here — for my daughters, and for me.</p>
      <p class="muted">Guided by five values: Mahalo, Aloha, Ohana, Pono, Imua.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="photo">
      <img src="/images/mission/eighteen.webp" alt="Airman Herrington" loading="lazy"
           onerror="this.parentElement.style.background='#dfe9f4'" />
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .becoming { background: var(--blue-50); }
  .becoming .kicker { color: var(--blue-s); }
  .becoming .wrap { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 38px; align-items: center; }
  .becoming h2 { font-size: 28px; margin-top: 12px; }
  .becoming p { margin-top: 13px; max-width: 520px; }
  .becoming .muted { color: var(--muted); }
  .becoming .photo {
    height: 300px; border-radius: 14px; overflow: hidden; border: 1px solid var(--line);
  }
  .becoming .photo img { width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover; display: block; }

  @media (max-width: 820px) { .becoming .wrap { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }
</style>
